parameters: Akane: I won't let you do any more...!!

Chancellor: Do you think a leftover small fry like you can
do anything?

Akane: It's no good here! But if you remain... surely, you
can make a difference!!

Akane: If you die, the country, even the princess,
everything will be over!!

I can't do it!! Leaving you all behind and fleeing from
here!!

Akane: The princess will surely wait for your return in her
slumber!!

Akane: You're our only hope! So please, I beg you!
Survive!!!
Chancellor: Tch... such a boring stunt...!!

Sorcerer: What shall we do about that one? Shall we send
pursuers immediately?
Chancellor: There's no need for that.

Chancellor: I have confirmed that the seed of the tentacle
has been planted in her. A special seed created from the
curse of the royal blood.
Chancellor: Even if left alone, she won't last much longer.
Chancellor: Now is truly our main event.
Chancellor: Now, Princess. Let us shed blood together.
Chancellor: Enough blood to dye this land, this moon, red!!!
